## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "CDK Application"
        A[Bucket Construct]
        C[Index Construct]
        E[KnowledgeBase Construct]
    end

    subgraph "AWS Cloud<br>"
        CR[CloudFormation<br>Custom Resources]
        G[Lambda Function]
        H[S3 Vectors API]
        I[Bedrock API]

        B[S3 Vector Bucket]
        D[S3 Vector Index]
        F[Bedrock Knowledge Base]
    end

    A -- defines --> CR
    C -- defines --> CR
    E -- defines --> CR

    CR -- invokes --> G

    G -- calls --> H
    G -- calls --> I

    H -- creates --> B
    H -- creates --> D
    I -- creates --> F
```

